@startuml
title Athena JS command docs before CLI-reference pass

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam Rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #FCE5CD
  BorderColor #B45F06
}
skinparam ArrowColor #7A7A7A

actor "Developer" as Dev

rectangle "README\n(partial CLI examples)" as Readme #FCE5CD
rectangle "docs/getting-started.md\n(generator basics)" as GettingStarted #FCE5CD
rectangle "docs/generator-config.md\nconfig + provider modes" as GeneratorConfig #FCE5CD
rectangle "No single command matrix\nor shim troubleshooting source" as Gap #F4CCCC

Dev --> Readme : find command hints
Dev --> GettingStarted : infer command usage
Dev --> GeneratorConfig : infer options/errors
Readme --> Gap
GettingStarted --> Gap
GeneratorConfig --> Gap

note right of Gap
CLI help behavior and Windows global-shim recovery
were spread across notes and terminal threads.
end note

@enduml
